   <titleInfo>
      <title>Adolescent And Young Adult Fathers: Problems And Solutions</title>
   </titleInfo>
   <abstract>This report addresses the financial responsibilities of adolescent and young adult fathers and ways to encourage financial responsibility in young fathers; statistcal data provides insight into the profile of the unwed adolescent father and explores ideas for programs and solutions to assist young fathers in providing financial resources for their children.</abstract>
